WEBVTT

00:31.280 --> 00:32.479
What are you thinking about?

00:33.680 --> 00:34.640
Nothing at all.

00:35.520 --> 00:37.840
Why does something smell burnt?

00:40.120 --> 00:41.560
My dish!

00:54.800 --> 00:56.120
What happened?

01:10.840 --> 01:12.480
Qian wants to borrow you as her husband.

01:14.280 --> 01:15.280
What?

01:16.360 --> 01:18.600
Soon as something's good,
people rush in to grab it!

01:18.680 --> 01:20.800
Borrow. She meant to borrow him.

01:21.560 --> 01:23.440
She needs him to scare off
an overbearing patron.

01:23.520 --> 01:25.320
Borrowing will not do!

01:25.400 --> 01:27.320
Zhao, why are you tugging at me?

01:27.400 --> 01:29.240
If some woman asked
to borrow you, would you agree?

01:30.000 --> 01:32.960
Well, if she were sweet enough,
I might consider it.

01:33.040 --> 01:34.960
Say that again! I dare you!

01:35.040 --> 01:36.240
What did she promise you?

01:36.320 --> 01:38.320
How much did you sell me for?

01:38.400 --> 01:40.800
As if I would sell you for a few taels.

01:40.880 --> 01:42.040
Yes, yes.

01:42.120 --> 01:44.040
A few taels would be far too cheap.

01:44.120 --> 01:45.320
Thirty taels.

01:46.480 --> 01:47.680
-What?
-Thirty taels?

01:51.680 --> 01:54.960
To be honest, Changyu truly means well.

01:55.040 --> 01:57.400
Yan Zheng, why not lend a hand?

01:57.480 --> 01:58.800
Think of it as earning merit.

01:58.880 --> 02:00.240
-But--
-No!

02:00.320 --> 02:01.760
No? No what?

02:01.840 --> 02:03.960
If someone offered a few taels,
I'd sell you on the spot!

02:04.040 --> 02:05.040
You…

02:06.080 --> 02:08.840
Changning, come. Let's not listen to them.

02:09.440 --> 02:11.600
I'm not worth as much as a pig?

02:11.680 --> 02:13.480
And how much do you think you are worth?

02:14.200 --> 02:15.520
Why not ask someone else?

02:15.600 --> 02:18.000
That Lord Li, for example.

02:18.920 --> 02:20.360
He has already left Lin'an.

02:24.880 --> 02:26.880
Even if he were here,
I would not go to him.

02:27.600 --> 02:29.240
Why seek help from an outsider

02:29.320 --> 02:30.960
when my husband stands before me?

02:36.600 --> 02:38.280
Just help Qian out.

02:38.360 --> 02:39.320
Only one day.

02:39.920 --> 02:41.120
If Yixiang Restaurant collapses,

02:41.200 --> 02:43.080
our business will suffer too.

02:43.920 --> 02:47.120
That rice merchant Qi
is like a medicinal plaster.

02:47.200 --> 02:48.520
Clings tight and will not come off.

02:49.200 --> 02:50.880
Does no real harm,
but makes one miserable.

02:52.240 --> 02:53.520
Rice merchant Qi?

02:55.520 --> 02:57.800
Has he been close
with anyone of note recently?

02:57.880 --> 03:00.080
A rice merchant from the capital,
surnamed Qi.

03:04.240 --> 03:05.160
One day?

03:05.240 --> 03:06.200
Only one.

04:33.800 --> 04:38.480
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:41.200 --> 04:43.760
GUESTS FROM ACROSS THE REALM

04:52.840 --> 04:54.800
-This way.
-Yan Zheng.

04:55.920 --> 04:57.960
Dressed like that, forget shopkeeper.

04:58.040 --> 05:00.240
You could pass for a marquis!

05:00.320 --> 05:02.040
Good. This way.

05:05.200 --> 05:07.120
Today we rely on you.

05:09.160 --> 05:10.400
Do not worry.

05:10.480 --> 05:13.320
Changyu said you are
her dearest friend in Lin'an.

05:14.120 --> 05:15.320
If she wishes to help you,

05:15.400 --> 05:16.600
I will not refuse.

05:18.600 --> 05:19.480
This way.

05:20.440 --> 05:22.760
‎TIANZI ROOM

05:24.800 --> 05:26.080
Mr. Qi!

05:30.200 --> 05:32.640
Ms. Yu, all better now?

05:34.400 --> 05:37.160
Mr. Qi, this is my husband, Yan Zheng.

05:57.400 --> 05:59.680
He has been away on business

05:59.760 --> 06:00.920
and just returned today.

06:01.000 --> 06:02.240
I brought him here to thank you

06:02.320 --> 06:04.320
for your support of our establishment.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.400
Mr. Qi.

06:07.240 --> 06:08.360
An honor.

06:09.760 --> 06:11.720
So you are Yu Qianqian's husband.

06:11.800 --> 06:13.000
Indeed.

06:26.840 --> 06:29.080
Yan Zheng, entertain Mr. Qi well.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.600
I'll go get some more wine and dishes.

06:37.400 --> 06:38.400
Mr. Qi.

06:39.160 --> 06:40.120
Please.

06:47.960 --> 06:49.680
When Master throws his cup,

06:49.760 --> 06:50.920
we seize him.

06:55.280 --> 06:57.840
I heard you were from the capital.

06:58.480 --> 07:00.920
What draws you to a small town like Lin'an

07:01.000 --> 07:02.240
to deal in grain?

07:05.840 --> 07:08.200
And you, Mr. Yan, are not a native either.

07:08.720 --> 07:11.480
Why open a restaurant here?

07:17.360 --> 07:20.200
My wife has not attended you properly.
Please forgive us.

07:21.240 --> 07:22.880
If there is business to be done,

07:22.960 --> 07:24.200
please come to me directly.

07:27.160 --> 07:30.360
And what scale of trade
can you manage, Mr. Yan?

07:34.000 --> 07:35.160
For instance,

07:37.120 --> 07:39.160
200,000 dan of grain.

07:57.360 --> 07:58.240
Forgive me.

08:01.120 --> 08:03.400
Our restaurant is doing roaring business.

08:04.560 --> 08:08.080
It's only natural that resentful rivals
would scheme against us

08:08.760 --> 08:10.000
in the shadows.

08:16.800 --> 08:18.400
No wonder Yu Qianqian

08:18.480 --> 08:20.560
declined my request
to rent out the restaurant.

08:21.600 --> 08:23.160
The offer wasn't generous enough.

08:23.760 --> 08:24.600
Very well.

08:25.560 --> 08:27.200
We shall speak another day.

08:37.960 --> 08:39.080
Where is he?

08:39.760 --> 08:41.480
-Gone.
-Gone?

08:42.840 --> 08:44.000
He gave up that easily?

08:44.800 --> 08:47.360
Yan Zheng, those 30 taels were well spent!

08:58.160 --> 08:59.560
What troubles you, Master?

09:02.680 --> 09:03.520
You would never guess.

09:04.400 --> 09:06.520
I just met a dead man walking.

09:06.600 --> 09:09.080
That woman called him her husband.

09:10.440 --> 09:11.760
You mean…

09:22.080 --> 09:25.040
Marquis Wu'an, Xie Zheng.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.360
Xie Zheng?

09:28.600 --> 09:30.280
Was he not dead?

09:34.080 --> 09:36.440
If Marquis Wu'an still lives,

09:36.520 --> 09:39.160
Prince Changxin's plan
will not unfold so easily.

09:41.400 --> 09:43.200
My dear father

09:43.280 --> 09:46.960
intended to start his game by using
bandits to rob the military grain,

09:47.040 --> 09:49.520
drive out refugees, spread panic,
then he could reap the benefits.

09:49.600 --> 09:50.840
But now,

09:51.360 --> 09:52.960
Marquis Wu'an lives.

09:53.040 --> 09:55.480
He even knows we purchased
200,000 dan of grain.

09:56.800 --> 09:58.720
Clearly, he was well prepared.

09:59.280 --> 10:02.040
Who will win remains uncertain.

10:02.560 --> 10:05.560
This game grows more interesting
by the moment.

10:08.280 --> 10:11.360
Master, you deliberately leaked word,

10:11.440 --> 10:14.160
drawing him to investigate
the Jinzhou massacre 16 years ago.

10:14.760 --> 10:17.080
You knew Wei Yan
would never reopen the case.

10:17.160 --> 10:18.720
You meant to borrow Wei Yan's hand

10:18.800 --> 10:20.720
to eliminate Xie Zheng,
the threat of yours.

10:21.640 --> 10:23.720
Yet he lives.

10:24.480 --> 10:26.520
Shall we quietly inform Wei Yan

10:26.600 --> 10:28.240
of his whereabouts

10:28.320 --> 10:29.760
and borrow another blade?

10:31.080 --> 10:31.920
No.

10:32.000 --> 10:33.800
I drove them into open conflict

10:33.880 --> 10:35.840
to strip him of his support.

10:36.360 --> 10:38.520
Marquis Wu'an has never been our enemy.

10:38.600 --> 10:42.200
Now that the rift between uncle
and nephew is beyond repair,

10:42.280 --> 10:44.160
the Marquis is lost and adrift
in such a village.

10:44.240 --> 10:46.040
This is the moment to win him over.

10:48.040 --> 10:49.560
Take my Crown Prince seal.

10:49.640 --> 10:52.120
Draw him out under my former title
of the Crown Prince.

10:53.560 --> 10:54.520
Yes.

10:57.560 --> 10:59.040
And Shopkeeper Yu Qianqian?

10:59.640 --> 11:00.600
Her?

11:03.680 --> 11:05.280
Keep her under watch.

11:06.560 --> 11:07.200
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

11:07.280 --> 11:09.280
This way, ladies.

11:10.840 --> 11:11.920
Inside, please.

11:12.480 --> 11:13.560
Honored guests, this way.

11:25.520 --> 11:26.520
Mrs. Fan.

11:35.520 --> 11:36.760
Changyu!

11:36.840 --> 11:37.800
Come here!

11:40.440 --> 11:41.280
Look at this place.

11:41.960 --> 11:43.120
So lively.

11:43.200 --> 11:44.160
It's all thanks to you!

11:44.240 --> 11:46.120
What do I have to do with it?

11:46.200 --> 11:48.280
Ever since your husband
paid us that visit,

11:48.360 --> 11:50.520
that rice merchant Qi
has not dared trouble me again.

11:51.040 --> 11:52.800
I can finally run my business in peace.

11:52.880 --> 11:54.000
This bustle?

11:54.080 --> 11:55.000
You deserve the credit.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.160
Come with me.

12:00.720 --> 12:03.280
I wonder what Chef Li is making
for Lunar New Year's Eve.

12:04.000 --> 12:05.600
What are you cooking tonight?

12:07.520 --> 12:08.760
Cabbage and tofu.

12:09.480 --> 12:11.000
-And stir-fried pork.
-Go on.

12:13.360 --> 12:15.320
Greetings, Mother. Mrs. Fan.

12:16.200 --> 12:17.040
Sit.

12:18.480 --> 12:20.240
What is Changning doing at home?

12:20.320 --> 12:21.240
I miss her!

12:21.840 --> 12:22.880
After Lunar New Year's Eve,

12:22.960 --> 12:24.800
why not come play at our house?

12:26.680 --> 12:28.320
Mother, may I?

12:30.640 --> 12:31.920
Very well.

12:32.000 --> 12:32.880
But only this time.

12:34.120 --> 12:36.720
Changning said she would show me
your family heirloom.

12:37.440 --> 12:39.800
Family heirloom…

12:43.440 --> 12:44.960
She means the butcher knife.

12:46.040 --> 12:47.360
Perhaps that is not necessary.

12:48.120 --> 12:49.160
That is marvelous!

12:49.240 --> 12:50.360
An actual butcher knife!

12:54.560 --> 12:56.360
Mrs. Fan and I have matters to discuss.

12:56.440 --> 12:57.280
Go study.

13:02.000 --> 13:03.000
Come on.

13:05.720 --> 13:06.960
Qian,

13:07.040 --> 13:09.120
are you not a bit strict with Bao'er?

13:10.560 --> 13:11.720
Not at all.

13:11.800 --> 13:13.240
I just want him to succeed.

13:16.400 --> 13:19.160
Changyu, tomorrow is Lunar New Year's Eve.

13:19.240 --> 13:21.120
You must be swamped.

13:21.760 --> 13:25.200
Let me wish you smooth fortunes
in the year ahead.

13:25.840 --> 13:28.360
I am not young anymore.
Why give me the red packet?

13:29.800 --> 13:32.920
We stay forever young!

13:33.000 --> 13:34.160
Come. Let's drink.

13:35.080 --> 13:36.480
Drinking at noon?

13:37.280 --> 13:39.920
Women drink by mood, not by time.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.160
If not now, when?

13:43.400 --> 13:47.400
AUSPICIOUS ABUNDANCE

13:48.240 --> 13:49.280
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

13:54.000 --> 13:54.880
Qian,

13:55.520 --> 13:57.880
the last time I felt this carefree

13:58.480 --> 14:00.960
was the day I married Yan Zheng.

14:04.440 --> 14:05.680
Changyu,

14:06.600 --> 14:09.280
you have been wed some time now.

14:10.560 --> 14:12.240
Tell me honestly. Are you satisfied

14:12.320 --> 14:13.200
with your husband?

14:17.520 --> 14:19.960
He is not all show
and no substance, is he?

14:20.960 --> 14:22.600
What nonsense.

14:23.680 --> 14:25.760
Yan Zheng is solid gold.

14:26.280 --> 14:28.640
Pure and true.

14:29.400 --> 14:30.720
That impressive?

14:31.960 --> 14:34.000
Then I shall go trash
that gossiping Kang right now!

14:34.080 --> 14:35.640
She swore you two
haven't even shared a bed!

14:37.560 --> 14:38.720
You mean consummated?

14:39.480 --> 14:40.600
What else?

14:41.120 --> 14:42.560
That foul mouth of hers.

14:42.640 --> 14:45.520
Do not worry. I can afford
the fine if I beat her up.

14:45.600 --> 14:46.920
Qian.

14:47.640 --> 14:49.400
To be fair,

14:50.200 --> 14:52.520
she was not entirely wrong.

14:55.160 --> 14:58.200
Which part?

15:00.320 --> 15:01.680
One day,

15:02.400 --> 15:06.080
Mrs. Zhao locked the two of us in a room.

15:07.400 --> 15:09.640
It seemed he wanted to kiss me.

15:11.760 --> 15:13.160
You ate candied tangerine peel?

15:13.880 --> 15:16.360
I can smell it on you.

15:17.000 --> 15:19.600
Right now, do you want some?

15:24.760 --> 15:25.600
And?

15:26.520 --> 15:28.240
And…

15:30.160 --> 15:31.560
We ended up fighting.

15:37.520 --> 15:39.200
So you two are serious.

15:48.200 --> 15:50.280
Deep down,

15:52.560 --> 15:53.520
I know…

15:56.400 --> 15:57.800
he'll leave one day.

16:01.920 --> 16:04.720
I have asked him more than once,
in roundabout ways.

16:08.440 --> 16:10.160
He has never changed his answer.

16:18.080 --> 16:20.160
Your husband

16:21.120 --> 16:22.880
seems to build
for something bigger than here.

16:26.760 --> 16:27.960
Do not worry.

16:28.040 --> 16:29.200
If he insists on leaving,

16:29.800 --> 16:32.320
then before he does, have his child.

16:33.040 --> 16:33.920
Think about it.

16:34.000 --> 16:36.160
If the child inherits his looks,

16:36.240 --> 16:37.520
that is a blessing.

16:41.160 --> 16:43.480
I can't do that.

16:44.920 --> 16:46.520
That sounds shameless.

16:48.080 --> 16:50.040
If you want the cub,
you must first catch the wolf.

16:50.120 --> 16:51.440
No.

16:51.520 --> 16:54.240
If you want the cub,
you must first feed the wolf.

16:58.960 --> 16:59.960
Relax.

17:00.040 --> 17:01.760
Leave it to me.

17:11.800 --> 17:16.240
XIGU ALLEY

17:24.920 --> 17:28.319
I, Zhao Xun of Lin'an Grain,
come for a visit.

17:32.240 --> 17:33.400
It is bitterly cold.

17:33.480 --> 17:35.520
Will Your Lordship not invite me inside?

17:45.440 --> 17:46.480
Marquis.

17:47.240 --> 17:48.200
Marquis?

17:48.720 --> 17:49.920
HAVE A FULL MEAL

17:56.840 --> 17:57.720
How did you recognize me?

17:59.320 --> 18:01.920
I once conducted business
in Jizhou and Yanzhou.

18:02.440 --> 18:04.080
I was fortunate enough
to witness your presence.

18:08.160 --> 18:09.440
So,

18:10.280 --> 18:12.320
what brings you here?

18:16.160 --> 18:17.800
The Xie family's loyalty

18:18.320 --> 18:20.480
is known throughout the realm.

18:21.240 --> 18:22.960
Yet Heaven shows little mercy.

18:23.040 --> 18:24.800
The loyal fall to treachery
time and again.

18:25.560 --> 18:27.680
I cannot help but feel injustice
on your behalf.

18:31.640 --> 18:32.920
Speak plainly.

18:34.000 --> 18:36.320
Were you not hunted by Wei Yan

18:36.920 --> 18:39.840
for reopening the Jinzhou massacre
of 16 years ago?

18:47.160 --> 18:48.880
Who are you?

19:04.960 --> 19:06.600
TREASURE SEAL OF CHENGDE

19:06.680 --> 19:08.320
Sixteen years ago,

19:09.160 --> 19:11.040
when fire consumed the Eastern Palace,

19:11.680 --> 19:13.360
I was among the few who survived.

19:15.360 --> 19:17.560
Wei Yan holds the court in his grip,

19:17.640 --> 19:19.280
propping up a puppet emperor.

19:19.360 --> 19:21.280
We are those

19:21.360 --> 19:23.080
who seek to set the realm right.

19:24.840 --> 19:28.240
And what proof do you offer?

19:29.440 --> 19:32.800
Sixteen years ago,
Crown Prince Chengde and your father

19:32.880 --> 19:34.880
both fell in Jinzhou.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.200
Soon after, the emperor abdicated.

19:37.280 --> 19:38.360
Then came the fire.

19:39.240 --> 19:41.600
Each thread points toward Wei Yan.

19:41.680 --> 19:44.320
Your father and the Crown Prince
died in battle,

19:44.400 --> 19:47.200
their bodies hung by the Northern Jue
on the city walls for days.

19:48.120 --> 19:50.360
Do you not wish to avenge that blood?

19:54.880 --> 19:57.960
The moment you resumed
the investigation of Jinzhou,

19:58.480 --> 19:59.840
assassins pursued you,

19:59.920 --> 20:01.440
driving you into exile.

20:01.520 --> 20:03.320
Is that not proof?

20:12.800 --> 20:13.760
It is not enough.

20:24.560 --> 20:25.640
We have learned

20:26.320 --> 20:27.960
Wei Yan dispatched his assassins

20:28.040 --> 20:29.960
across one capital and 17 prefectures,

20:30.040 --> 20:30.960
killing a dozen men.

20:32.680 --> 20:34.960
All were former retainers
who once served him

20:35.040 --> 20:36.720
and later withdrew from his service.

20:36.800 --> 20:38.800
What does the Fan family possess

20:38.880 --> 20:41.480
that would warrant the Wei clan's
Xuan Tie death warriors?

20:41.560 --> 20:42.960
It's the Chancellor.

20:43.520 --> 20:44.920
He ordered me to retrieve a letter.

20:46.440 --> 20:49.280
So Fan Erniu once served Wei Yan.

20:49.920 --> 20:52.040
That explains the relentless pursuit.

20:52.720 --> 20:53.760
Marquis, Wei Yan's power

20:54.560 --> 20:55.800
overshadows the court.

20:56.440 --> 20:57.920
He seeks to eclipse the throne.

20:58.720 --> 21:00.320
If you wish to move a man like that,

21:00.400 --> 21:02.280
can you truly do it alone?

21:03.200 --> 21:04.960
And why should I trust you?

21:05.040 --> 21:06.880
Then tell me.
What would make you believe me?

21:09.520 --> 21:10.880
Offer me a token first.

21:11.520 --> 21:12.560
A token?

21:14.640 --> 21:16.280
Two hundred thousand dan of grain.

21:17.320 --> 21:18.240
Deal?

21:21.840 --> 21:24.000
It seems he truly knows

21:24.080 --> 21:27.040
about our grain purchases
in Jizhou and Chongzhou.

21:28.640 --> 21:30.200
We acquired it
through layers of merchants.

21:30.280 --> 21:32.960
At least a hundred hands
touched that grain.

21:33.040 --> 21:34.800
How could he know the number so precisely?

21:35.400 --> 21:39.000
That is precisely what I would ask you.

21:40.160 --> 21:42.360
Master, forgive me. I failed you.

21:44.840 --> 21:46.680
Still, the fact that he named
a price is encouraging.

21:46.760 --> 21:48.240
This is business.

21:49.520 --> 21:51.400
Once a price is spoken,
terms can be shaped.

21:54.720 --> 21:56.280
Two hundred thousand dan…

21:56.840 --> 21:57.760
Master,

21:57.840 --> 22:01.000
we have nearly emptied the granaries
of Chongzhou and Jizhou these past months.

22:01.800 --> 22:03.560
No one said we must
deliver it all at once.

22:06.640 --> 22:09.160
Father has never truly valued me.

22:09.240 --> 22:11.640
Even the title of heir
is meant for Sui Yuanqing.

22:12.240 --> 22:14.880
But if Marquis Wu'an stands with us,

22:15.920 --> 22:17.680
the odds will shift in our favor.

22:18.320 --> 22:21.760
What if Marquis Wu'an
doesn't follow our plan,

22:21.840 --> 22:24.240
takes the grain, then turns against us?

22:24.840 --> 22:26.200
Turns against us?

22:26.280 --> 22:27.600
Where could he possibly go?

22:28.400 --> 22:30.240
Back into Wei Yan's service?

22:31.560 --> 22:34.120
If he truly aids me,

22:34.200 --> 22:35.640
let alone 200,000 dan of grain,

22:35.720 --> 22:37.280
the four prefectures of the northwest

22:37.360 --> 22:39.120
will be my reward to him.

22:39.200 --> 22:40.600
Understood.

22:40.680 --> 22:42.200
I will see it done.

22:52.200 --> 22:54.080
Wei Yan…

22:55.880 --> 23:00.000
Soon, the wolf you raised

23:00.920 --> 23:02.320
will bare its teeth at you.

23:06.000 --> 23:07.160
Chancellor.

23:07.680 --> 23:10.920
While investigating Li Xing's contacts
with the rebel faction,

23:11.800 --> 23:12.960
we uncovered something else.

23:13.040 --> 23:15.560
Marquis Wu'an's inquiry
into the Jinzhou case 16 years ago

23:16.560 --> 23:19.720
started on the leaks
from Prince Changxin's household.

23:22.880 --> 23:26.040
They removed Xie Zheng

23:27.040 --> 23:30.920
so that Prince Changxin would have
one less greatest obstacle at the front.

23:32.280 --> 23:34.280
The Sui clan

23:35.120 --> 23:37.280
is undermining my plans.

23:41.200 --> 23:42.280
There is another matter.

23:42.360 --> 23:44.080
Li Xing has summoned Li Huai'an

23:44.160 --> 23:45.280
back to the capital.

23:47.240 --> 23:48.800
The Grand Princess has returned as well.

23:48.880 --> 23:51.520
That old fox likely intends
to secure a marriage,

23:52.400 --> 23:55.200
so he hastily recalled
his eldest grandson.

23:57.120 --> 23:58.200
Leave it.

23:59.520 --> 24:01.680
Send word to He Jingyuan at once.

24:01.760 --> 24:03.840
Tell him to hold Lucheng at all costs.

24:03.920 --> 24:05.720
That will be the field of reckoning.

24:07.560 --> 24:13.680
LUNAR NEW YEAR'S EVE

24:20.240 --> 24:21.600
Happy Lunar New Year!

24:21.680 --> 24:22.800
Come, everyone, eat!

24:22.880 --> 24:24.360
Coming!

24:24.440 --> 24:25.920
Mrs. Wang, Happy Lunar New Year!

24:26.440 --> 24:28.040
FORTUNE

24:28.120 --> 24:29.080
Look at me!

24:29.800 --> 24:32.040
-Happy Lunar New Year!
-Happy Lunar New Year, Uncle!

24:32.120 --> 24:33.280
Happy Lunar New Year!

24:34.520 --> 24:35.360
Happy Lunar New Year!

24:35.440 --> 24:36.960
SPRING BREEZE TOFU SHOP

24:38.920 --> 24:40.480
That's it. Keep going.

24:41.080 --> 24:42.120
A horizontal stroke.

24:42.840 --> 24:44.200
Now vertical.

24:45.600 --> 24:46.640
Vertical.

24:48.040 --> 24:50.640
Horizontal, turn, sweep left, sweep right.

24:58.040 --> 25:00.920
Changyu, Zheng is teaching me to write!

25:01.000 --> 25:02.080
Good girl.

25:07.120 --> 25:09.280
Can you write couplets?

25:11.920 --> 25:15.680
Mother used to write ours every year.

25:15.760 --> 25:17.400
Zheng, can you write couplets?

25:18.440 --> 25:19.560
Bring the paper.

25:19.640 --> 25:20.560
All right.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.680
Too much ink.

25:40.080 --> 25:41.720
Then we will write a few extra.

25:41.800 --> 25:43.360
One for Mr. and Mrs. Zhao.

25:44.120 --> 25:46.680
And paste them on every doorframe.

25:46.760 --> 25:47.840
More red, more joy.

25:49.120 --> 25:50.000
Very well.

26:32.360 --> 26:34.960
Did I… Did I bump you?

26:35.480 --> 26:37.280
It is nothing. Just too much ink.

26:43.240 --> 26:45.480
‎BE KIND, DO GOOD

26:45.560 --> 26:46.960
This is beautiful.

26:51.280 --> 26:52.320
Such a pity.

26:53.400 --> 26:54.640
It is no matter.

26:55.760 --> 26:57.840
We will hang them on our room door.

26:59.360 --> 27:01.400
Ice… something.

27:02.360 --> 27:03.480
Spring… something.

27:05.480 --> 27:09.680
Snow… something. Grass… something.

27:10.560 --> 27:12.240
"Ice melts, the springs pulse.

27:12.320 --> 27:13.960
Snow clears, young grass rises."

27:15.800 --> 27:19.120
When my mother wrote
Spring Festival couplets,

27:19.200 --> 27:22.240
she never liked writing
the same old blessings either.

27:22.920 --> 27:23.840
You prefer this?

27:49.360 --> 27:50.200
You paint as well?

27:53.000 --> 27:54.200
A little.

28:01.120 --> 28:02.320
That is more than enough.

28:05.040 --> 28:06.360
You could make good money

28:07.120 --> 28:08.720
selling your art.

28:13.080 --> 28:14.840
I don't create against my will.

28:17.880 --> 28:20.000
I want to write too!

28:22.240 --> 28:23.800
Then write the horizontal scroll.

28:25.480 --> 28:27.480
Come, Ning, write it.

28:29.720 --> 28:31.160
What shall we write?

28:32.200 --> 28:33.440
What shall we write?

28:45.080 --> 28:46.320
Let's write this.

28:52.920 --> 28:54.720
CERTAINLY RICH

28:54.800 --> 28:55.880
How is that?

28:59.520 --> 29:00.640
It is like

29:01.920 --> 29:03.320
adding a dog's tail to a sable coat.

29:06.520 --> 29:07.880
That means it is very good, yes?

29:12.880 --> 29:14.480
That means it is very good, yes?

29:16.720 --> 29:17.840
Perfectly fitting.

29:22.440 --> 29:24.360
It's only because I wrote it so well!

29:24.440 --> 29:25.600
I'm amazing!

29:27.840 --> 29:30.000
Oh! We forgot the falcon.

29:35.520 --> 29:36.920
Falcon, be good.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.560
We celebrate Lunar New Year together!

29:43.760 --> 29:45.560
Press its claw here.

29:45.640 --> 29:48.280
Now our family is complete.

29:52.600 --> 29:53.600
Look.

29:56.520 --> 29:57.520
Zhao.

29:57.600 --> 29:59.240
Lower it a little.

30:00.120 --> 30:01.000
All right. Good!

30:01.080 --> 30:02.480
Don't move! That's good.

30:02.560 --> 30:03.880
-All right.
-Let's look at Changyu's house.

30:06.280 --> 30:07.160
Perfect!

30:09.280 --> 30:10.280
Honey.

30:10.800 --> 30:11.920
How is the writing?

30:12.000 --> 30:13.160
Beautiful.

30:13.240 --> 30:15.760
-I have never seen writing so fine.
-Her husband wrote these, right?

30:15.840 --> 30:18.920
-He did.
-You, who cannot read, can tell?

30:19.000 --> 30:20.240
I may not read,

30:20.320 --> 30:22.440
but I know worth when I see it.

30:22.520 --> 30:24.760
Look at those strokes. Square and steady.

30:24.840 --> 30:26.800
That hand is worth silver!

30:27.480 --> 30:29.440
Mr. and Mrs. Zhao,

30:29.520 --> 30:31.560
these couplets are splendid!

30:31.640 --> 30:32.560
Who wrote them?

30:32.640 --> 30:34.800
Changyu's husband did.

30:36.480 --> 30:37.600
By the way…

30:38.640 --> 30:39.480
Mr. Fan!

30:42.120 --> 30:43.040
Changyu!

30:43.720 --> 30:46.120
Your husband's couplets are excellent!

30:46.200 --> 30:49.040
Better than the ones Song Yan

30:49.120 --> 30:50.440
used to write.

30:50.520 --> 30:51.360
See?

30:51.440 --> 30:53.200
Our Changyu's got an eye for people.

30:54.600 --> 30:56.240
Write one for me too, will you?

30:59.000 --> 31:00.840
-Yes, yes, do ours as well.
-Write for all of us.

31:00.920 --> 31:02.840
Aunties, forgive us,

31:02.920 --> 31:04.560
but we've run out of red paper.

31:05.520 --> 31:06.840
That's no matter.

31:06.920 --> 31:08.920
We've never been short
of red paper at home.

31:09.880 --> 31:11.320
We've got some at home too.

31:11.400 --> 31:13.120
-So do we.
-We do too.

31:13.200 --> 31:14.040
All right.

31:14.560 --> 31:16.160
Bring it over.

31:16.240 --> 31:17.520
All right!

31:17.600 --> 31:18.800
Let's go fetch the red paper.

31:18.880 --> 31:19.800
Thank you.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.520
We'll be right back!

31:21.600 --> 31:22.600
Come on.

31:31.920 --> 31:32.840
You don't have to agree

31:32.920 --> 31:34.440
if you don't feel like it.

31:34.520 --> 31:35.480
Don't do it because of me.

31:36.680 --> 31:37.560
I want to.

31:39.720 --> 31:41.280
Just now, you said

31:41.360 --> 31:43.160
you wouldn't create against your will.

31:46.520 --> 31:48.160
-And now it suits you?
-Stop it.

31:48.240 --> 31:49.240
Grind the ink.

31:50.080 --> 31:50.920
Changyu.

31:51.440 --> 31:52.720
Madam Zhuang.

31:52.800 --> 31:54.440
I made some rice candy at home

31:54.520 --> 31:56.000
for little Ning to snack on.

31:57.080 --> 31:58.200
-Oh…
-Take it.

31:58.280 --> 32:01.480
We heard your husband's
writing spring couplets.

32:01.560 --> 32:03.600
Ours aren't done yet,

32:04.200 --> 32:06.440
so we shamelessly followed along.

32:06.960 --> 32:09.040
Didn't bring much.

32:09.120 --> 32:12.200
Just some freshly pressed tofu
for you to try.

32:14.040 --> 32:15.320
Aunties,

32:15.400 --> 32:16.280
have a seat first.

32:16.360 --> 32:17.360
All right, all right.

32:19.120 --> 32:20.440
-Thank you.
-Here's the red paper.

32:20.520 --> 32:21.520
Good, thank you.

32:42.920 --> 32:46.360
"Peace within the home,
calm on every side."

32:46.440 --> 32:48.000
-Beautiful handwriting.
-All right.

32:48.080 --> 32:49.040
Finished.

32:49.120 --> 32:50.480
Nicely written.

32:51.320 --> 32:53.200
"Lanterns at every door,
blessings for the new year.

32:53.280 --> 32:56.160
Oxen shoulder the spring,
plowing green fields."

32:56.240 --> 32:58.080
It means when spring comes,

32:58.160 --> 32:59.480
the harvest will be rich,

32:59.560 --> 33:01.000
and the family will live in peace.

33:04.680 --> 33:06.160
That's beautifully written.

33:09.920 --> 33:11.080
"When storms darken the sky,

33:11.160 --> 33:12.160
the rooster still crows.

33:12.240 --> 33:12.960
THE BOOK OF SONGS: AIRS OF ZHENG

33:13.040 --> 33:14.440
Having seen the graceful one,

33:14.520 --> 33:15.720
how could I not rejoice?"

33:16.720 --> 33:17.760
These lines speak

33:17.840 --> 33:20.760
of storm and turmoil, rain pouring,

33:20.840 --> 33:22.360
the world unsettled.

33:23.480 --> 33:26.120
Yet in the midst of all that confusion,

33:26.920 --> 33:28.440
you lift your eyes,

33:29.560 --> 33:30.920
and suddenly, there she is.

33:32.000 --> 33:34.680
Like clouds parting,

33:34.760 --> 33:37.040
a shaft of light falls over you.

33:39.000 --> 33:40.280
Warm. Bright.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.800
And joy rises from somewhere inside.

33:43.920 --> 33:45.600
When he recited it before,

33:46.200 --> 33:47.680
I only thought it sounded nice.

33:47.760 --> 33:49.680
I never understood why it was good.

33:51.320 --> 33:52.640
Until just now.

33:53.560 --> 33:56.120
He turned and looked at me.

33:57.840 --> 33:59.560
In that moment,

33:59.640 --> 34:01.280
the courtyard went quiet.

34:02.880 --> 34:06.760
Even the snow seemed to fall softer.

34:08.080 --> 34:09.120
The wind stopped biting.

34:09.920 --> 34:12.360
It felt like the winter sun,

34:13.520 --> 34:15.560
not too strong, not too weak,

34:15.639 --> 34:17.000
just right,

34:17.679 --> 34:21.239
resting squarely on me.

34:22.080 --> 34:24.239
When someone is truly happy,

34:24.320 --> 34:25.920
their heart makes a sound.

34:26.960 --> 34:29.120
Like sitting by the stove,

34:29.639 --> 34:31.600
hearing the firewood crackle.

34:32.280 --> 34:35.280
Soft, scattered pops. Small but warm.

34:38.440 --> 34:40.520
-Such beautiful writing.
-Those characters are elegant.

34:41.040 --> 34:42.239
Happy Lunar New Year!

34:42.840 --> 34:43.880
Your hand must be sore.

34:44.760 --> 34:45.679
It's nothing.

34:46.199 --> 34:47.360
Stubborn.

35:07.680 --> 35:08.920
You want couplets too?

35:12.760 --> 35:13.840
In the past,

35:14.920 --> 35:18.040
my eldest grandson, Kang Dan,
wrote the couplets.

35:18.640 --> 35:20.200
Then he got into trouble

35:20.280 --> 35:21.760
and was taken away for labor duty.

35:22.320 --> 35:23.560
After that,

35:24.320 --> 35:26.200
Song Yan helped us.

35:27.880 --> 35:30.840
Well, Kang Dan's 18 this year.

35:30.920 --> 35:32.760
Timid. A bit slow.

35:33.560 --> 35:35.880
I only hope my younger one, Kang Hu,

35:36.480 --> 35:39.520
grows up sharper than his brother.

35:41.640 --> 35:42.680
In the end,

35:43.240 --> 35:44.960
what does a person live for,

35:45.040 --> 35:46.960
if not a little hope?

35:53.440 --> 35:56.160
Maybe next year, or the year after,

35:56.240 --> 35:58.840
maybe things will turn around.

36:10.120 --> 36:11.080
Sit.

36:16.840 --> 36:18.440
What would you like written?

36:21.640 --> 36:23.800
Just… no more fighting.

36:24.480 --> 36:26.080
Leave my family a bloodline

36:26.160 --> 36:27.120
to carry on.

36:29.760 --> 36:31.120
Let my two grandsons,

36:32.120 --> 36:33.960
who have no parents to protect them,

36:34.680 --> 36:36.040
grow up safe and sound.

36:46.320 --> 36:47.240
All right.

36:56.720 --> 36:57.880
POISE AND REFINEMENT

37:15.200 --> 37:20.200
CASTING OFF SPLENDOR

37:22.640 --> 37:23.880
I pay my respects, Mother.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.960
You wished to see me.

37:27.040 --> 37:28.080
May I ask why?

37:32.040 --> 37:34.000
Lunar New Year's Eve
is a time for family reunion.

37:34.720 --> 37:36.760
Must I have a formal reason

37:36.840 --> 37:38.200
to see my daughter?

37:39.640 --> 37:41.040
That was not my intent.

37:48.160 --> 37:51.360
I pray the new year brings Mother

37:51.440 --> 37:54.080
peace, health, and lasting fortune.

37:58.920 --> 38:01.360
You and Marquis Wu'an were betrothed
before you were born.

38:02.160 --> 38:04.400
When he was alive, he was a rising star.

38:04.480 --> 38:06.720
Victorious in battle,
admired across the realm.

38:06.800 --> 38:09.400
Such a man would have been an ideal match.

38:10.360 --> 38:12.880
Yet you insisted you saw him
only as a brother

38:12.960 --> 38:14.320
and would not take him as consort.

38:16.080 --> 38:18.400
And now? An unfinished game of chess

38:18.480 --> 38:19.800
has unsettled your heart.

38:21.760 --> 38:23.120
Mother, what are you implying?

38:23.840 --> 38:25.520
Since returning to the palace,

38:25.600 --> 38:28.880
you have repeatedly claimed illness
to avoid meeting Li Huai'an.

38:28.960 --> 38:30.720
I have already arranged

38:30.800 --> 38:34.120
for you to attend
the Lantern Festival together.

38:35.160 --> 38:36.360
Mother!

38:37.360 --> 38:39.240
The Gongsuns have never sat
on the Grand Council.

38:41.240 --> 38:43.800
That is imperial decree.
It cannot be defied.

38:43.880 --> 38:45.360
You are the Grand Princess.

38:45.440 --> 38:47.120
You must not let a private attachment

38:47.200 --> 38:49.520
undermine the greater design
of the throne.

38:53.160 --> 38:55.000
I am not a piece on your board.

38:55.600 --> 38:57.920
I will not be arranged
for the sake of palace calculations!

38:58.000 --> 39:00.320
In your eyes,
there is only family prestige

39:00.400 --> 39:01.320
and imperial protocol.

39:01.400 --> 39:04.200
Have you ever once asked
what brings me happiness or sorrow?

39:05.360 --> 39:06.680
From this day forward,

39:06.760 --> 39:09.320
you are not to see anyone
from the Gongsun household again.

39:10.400 --> 39:12.480
Put an end to this at once.

39:16.760 --> 39:18.200
If there is nothing further,

39:18.840 --> 39:20.160
I shall take my leave.

39:23.320 --> 39:24.200
Shu!

39:25.120 --> 39:26.720
Your Highness, where are you going?

39:28.000 --> 39:29.680
To hang myself.

39:29.760 --> 39:30.800
Care to join me, Nanny?

39:42.080 --> 39:45.720
Tender words may weigh upon the heart,

39:47.760 --> 39:51.320
yet the bird still longs to soar.

40:06.440 --> 40:07.920
Let's eat!

40:08.600 --> 40:09.840
Go on.

40:09.920 --> 40:11.760
-Smells incredible!
-Smells good.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.240
Thank you.

40:13.840 --> 40:14.760
Here.

40:15.320 --> 40:17.000
-So good.
-Delicious.

40:17.920 --> 40:19.720
-Have more.
-So good.

40:19.800 --> 40:20.960
Coming.

40:23.520 --> 40:25.640
-Happy Lunar New Year!
-Happy Lunar New Year!

40:39.600 --> 40:41.680
-Another cup.
-Fill it!

40:41.760 --> 40:43.640
-Go on, fill it.
-I'll have some too.

40:44.800 --> 40:47.120
-Drink!
-No. You're still recovering.

40:47.800 --> 40:49.000
It's just light rice wine.

40:49.640 --> 40:50.480
Tea for you.

40:50.560 --> 40:53.520
The doctor said no alcohol
until you're fully healed.

40:53.600 --> 40:55.160
I want some too!

40:55.880 --> 40:57.480
You don't drink either.

40:57.560 --> 40:59.640
Come. Tea with your brother-in-law.

41:05.560 --> 41:07.600
-Eat well. Stay safe!
-Eat well. Stay safe.

41:07.680 --> 41:09.480
Drink up!

41:09.560 --> 41:10.440
Come.

41:22.760 --> 41:24.000
Yan Zheng.

41:25.560 --> 41:26.760
Maybe we could--

41:29.320 --> 41:30.320
Fireworks!

41:32.200 --> 41:34.720
-Look!
-Wow!

41:35.560 --> 41:36.600
Let's go see!

41:36.680 --> 41:38.280
-Come on.
-Fireworks!

41:41.840 --> 41:42.760
Slow down, Ning.

41:43.960 --> 41:46.080
What were you about to say?
I didn't hear you.

41:52.720 --> 41:54.680
I said I want more wine.

41:57.720 --> 41:59.720
-Come on. Upstairs.
-We'll see better from there.

42:00.640 --> 42:01.560
So beautiful!

42:01.640 --> 42:03.680
-It is good wine.
-Don't drink too much.

42:04.600 --> 42:05.880
I'm perfectly fine.

42:05.960 --> 42:07.840
This hardly counts as wine.

42:10.400 --> 42:11.320
Have some tea.

42:12.520 --> 42:13.560
It sobers you up.

42:21.760 --> 42:22.960
You think I can't handle it?

42:27.120 --> 42:28.680
Father could down a whole jar of liquor.

42:28.760 --> 42:30.120
I could manage half.

42:42.720 --> 42:44.360
This doesn't even make me dizzy.

42:44.440 --> 42:45.640
Come. Bottoms up.

42:48.080 --> 42:49.280
Come on.

42:54.520 --> 42:56.040
You're drunk.

42:58.480 --> 43:00.160
Not in the slightest.

43:02.320 --> 43:03.480
Happy Lunar New Year.

43:04.080 --> 43:05.120
Happy Lunar New Year.

43:19.280 --> 43:21.600
If you won't feed the wolf,

43:21.680 --> 43:23.720
you won't catch the cub…

43:25.840 --> 43:26.680
What cub?

43:46.800 --> 43:49.640
FESTIVE LANTERNS

46:16.440 --> 46:19.640
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:19.720 --> 46:20.600
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
